  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This 6-month project (2017) project consists of 1 component:
Component 1:  Provide emergency food assistance to the most vulnerable people in Askira Uba LGA in Borno State. 
This component will be delivered through 3 main activities namely: unconditional cash transfers, referral of severe acute malnourished (SAM) to hospitals, and distribution of RUTFS to under 5s with moderate malnutrition.</narrative>
